,"msg":"問題係有幾可真係會斷<br />\n但無線就好多個人因素會斷，而唔關供需事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T16:51:27.000Z","msg":"就咁講打機啦 咁短距離都係lan線好過WiFi"},{"pid":"d3f124453c3b76b6cd0307bc1655a2c9ef3b6600","tid":721063,"uid":123308,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T16:59:47.000Z","msg":"技術上我相信可行<br />\n<br />\n基站與基站，與及連接機樓／HKIX(2) 就一定係 optical fibre<br />\n至於基站至用戶，就係 5G radio<br />\n<br />\n但問題係<br />\n1. 就算理論值 5G 去到幾快都好，網絡商應該會限速／QoS，否則好易畀一（群）人 chur 盡個 bandwidth<br />\n<br />\n2. serve 嗰區嘅基站係唔係可以 serve 咁大容量嘅 users（涉及 bandwidth modulation / designed maximum capacity）<br />\n<br />\n3. 應該會有 data cap（可能每月 10GB，之後 128Kbps），以防有人 BT 掛機掛成晚<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講開又講，外國即使係家居寬頻都有 data cap<br />\n香港家居寬頻無限上網算係唔錯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外早期 Netvigator 如無記錯係每月 200 小時寬頻 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f42d5c9a31385984d40d7032a2f3857d65739540","tid":721063,"uid":182786,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T17:01:03.000Z","msg":"CSL 4G都吹到600速<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf8be9cce4c5ce6de6d5d25a0daf051346298610","tid":721063,"uid":376,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f42d5c9a31385984d40d7032a2f3857d65739540","tid":721063,"uid":182786,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T17:01:03.000Z","msg":"CSL 4G都吹到600速<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T17:03:50.000Z","msg":"有60都偷笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a12b9c78453dac0c6b14cdc1495bfbdb2802ccbb","tid":721063,"uid":5499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T17:46:30.000Z","msg":"一定係lan 線穩定d<br />\n<br />\n而且多條線又唔會阻到你"},{"pid":"6390d8e181d0f351cee1b6fbbbd66d3a659bc9e0","tid":721063,"uid":43575,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"a12b9c78453dac0c6b14cdc1495bfbdb2802ccbb","